_json.gridTitle: Homestead Layout Plans on 1 Acre or Less
_json.description: Homestead Layout Plans on 1 Acre or Less. You want to start homesteading but don’t have a lot of land? Lack of land is one of the biggest excuses that I hear from people who’d like to become more self-sufficient but just don’t get started. I hear you, because I also used to believe that homesteading required tons of land! That’s why I want to share these tiny homestead layouts with you.
